headline: Sombre Fundamentals Suggest General Mills Stock (GIS) is Stuck in a Value Trap
summary: Not so long ago, General Mills (GIS) stock was synonymous with safety, defensiveness, and stability. The company consistently delivered results in line with market expectations, rewarding shareholders with a generous and growing dividend. The snacking category, once an exception among packaged food groups, seemed immune to changing eating habits and the rise of private-label brands. But things have taken a turn for the worse.
